## ğŸ¯ Suggestions for AtliQ  
- **Smarter Marketing** â†’ Focus campaigns on high-return products & customers.  
- **Customer Negotiations** â†’ Especially Novus, align discounts with long-term value.  
- **Demand Planning** â†’ Refine forecasting to reduce Net Error & ABS Error.  
